Now that all the JS and CSS resources go through the new web resources framework, we have a whole lot of downloads queued up when the page loads.

We need to find a way to optimise this, either by combining resources together, or by optimising the download strategy in some other way.

Obviously the combining needs to be somewhat dynamic, not hard-coded on the server side.

